ed from freelancers and maintain accurate records\nRow 12: S.N.: 12 | Frequency: Regular | Activity Area: Vendor Bills Add | Detailed Tasks: Record and post daily vendor bills into the accounting system with appropriate cost heads\nRow 13: S.N.: 13 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: 2A Bills Add for TDS | Detailed Tasks: Enter and reconcile 2A bills in books on every 4th days of month\nRow 14: S.N.: 14 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: 2A Bills File Followup | Detailed Tasks: Follow up with vendors for timely filing and availability of 2A data\nRow 15: S.N.: 15 | Frequency: Weekly | Activity Area: Bank Statement Import and Closing Match | Detailed Tasks: Import bank statements and perform closing balance reconciliation across all accounts\nRow 16: S.N.: 16 | Frequency: Weekly | Activity Area: Documents Filling | Detailed Tasks: Organize, scan, and file all financial and operational documents in designated folders\nRow 17: S.N.: 17 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: 2B Bills add for GST return | Detailed Tasks: Enter and reconcile 2B bills in the books as on 14th every month\nRow 18: S.N.: 18 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: 2B Bills File Followup | Detailed Tasks: Follow up with tax consultants/vendors for timely filing and availability of 2B data\nRow 19: S.N.: 19 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: Vendors Mail For Bills ITC | Detailed Tasks: Initiate vendor communication requesting timely GST filing to ensure eligible Input Tax Credit\nRow 20: S.N.: 20 | Frequency: Weekly | Activity Area: Vendors Mail For Bills ITC Followup | Detailed Tasks: Send follow-up communications to vendors for submission of pending ITC-eligible bills\nRow 21: S.N.: 21 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: Vendor Statement Check | Detailed Tasks: Verify and reconcile vendor account statements with books\nRow 22: S.N.: 22 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: Tds Payable Sheet data Entering | Detailed Tasks: Compile and enter TDS payable data into the TDS worksheet for monthly sheet\nRow 23: S.N.: 23 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: Nayab 2B Bills Add | Detailed Tasks: Record and update 2B bills for Nayab\nRow 24: S.N.: 24 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: Nayab 2B Reconcilation | Detailed Tasks: Perform 2B reconciliation for Nayab\nRow 25: S.N.: 25 | Frequency: Monthly | Activity Area: Nayab Employee Salary Bills Creation | Detailed Tasks: Prepare and process salary bill creation for Nayab employees on a monthly basis\nRow 26: S.N.: 26 | Frequency: Regular | Activity Area: Vendor payment sheet Prepare | Detailed Tasks: The sheet prepare for the vendor payment management, guide by vibhav sir",
